Get even more out of Roblox.   Deck out your avatar and unlock additional perks in your favorite experiences when you use Roblox Gift Cards to purchase Robux (Roblox's virtual currency).   Or get exclusive access to virtual items, a monthly Robux stipend, and more by redeeming your gift card for a Roblox Premium subscription.   Each gift card grants an exclusive virtual item upon redemption.   Roblox is a global platform where every day millions of people come together to explore, chat, and hang out in millions of immersive 3D experiences created by the community.